  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A randomized, open-label, single-dose, crossover clinical trial to evaluate the food effect
      on the pharmacokinetics of DP-R202 tablet after oral administration in healthy male
      volunteers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The number of patient is twenty-four.Patients were randomly assigned either
      DP-R202(Sarpogrelate HCL 300mg, qd) under fasting condition or DP-R202(Sarpogrelate HCL
      300mg, qd) after eating foods.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
